            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Very bad experience, they function with BMC standards, staff is very rude and there is a lot of communication gap, where as academics concerned teachers dont teach up to the mark, last moment portion complete, some teachers assume that students go for classes therefore no need to teach properly. There is no grooming of the student.Office staff and other support staff is very rude. They don't talk politely they talk as if they are doing some favour on us. No events are properly organised. We are bound to enroll our children for good classes paying huge amount of fees. Class rooms are loaded with student, children cannot sit comfortably. No hygiene, If you really want your child to be a good human being please dont enroll your child to this school that is if you have good financial background. Academics is you can study at home we send our children to groom and socialise and other good qualities.",
          "publisher": {
